squo;\u00eatre incomprise ou inadapt\u00e9e. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Les z\u00e8bres se sentent souvent en d\u00e9calage avec leur environnement, ne savent pas \u00ab&nbsp;comment faire&nbsp;\u00bb avec les autres, bref, se sentent nuls\u2026<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Un accompagnement adapt\u00e9 permet de trouver des solutions pour bien vivre avec cette diff\u00e9rence.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Surdou\u00e9, Z\u00e8bre, Haut Potentiel (HP), Enfant Intellectuellement Pr\u00e9coce (EIP), &#8230; autant de terme pour la m\u00eame r\u00e9alit\u00e9 ! \u00catre \u00e0 Haut Potentiel c\u2019est disposer en g\u00e9n\u00e9ral d\u2019une grande intelligence, d\u2019une puissance singuli\u00e8re de la pens\u00e9e, d\u2019une certaine rapidit\u00e9 d\u2019analyse, de compr\u00e9hension, d\u2019une m\u00e9moire qui peut \u00eatre impressionnante \u2026 C&rsquo;est une forme d\u2019intelligence diff\u00e9rente, quantitativement, mais [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":330,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.laetitia-maltese.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/328"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.laetitia-maltese.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.laetitia-maltese.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.laetitia-maltese.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.laetitia-maltese.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=328"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/www.laetitia-maltese.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/328\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":334,"href":"https:\/\/www.laetitia-maltese.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/328\/revisions\/334"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\